HEADWORD: Scortatory
<hw>Scor"ta*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>scortator</ets> a fornicator, from <ets>scortari</ets> to
fornicate, <ets>scortum</ets> a prostitute.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to
lewdness or fornication; lewd.</def>⟦br⟧
